19
00:00:18,523 --> 00:00:20,942
<i>Divided by war,</i>

20
00:00:20,983 --> 00:00:23,528
<i>in an effort to end the Galactic conflict,</i>

21
00:00:23,611 --> 00:00:25,112
<i>the first ever sanctioned meeting</i>

22
00:00:25,196 --> 00:00:27,823
<i>between the Republic
and the Separatists will be held.</i>

23
00:00:27,907 --> 00:00:30,451
<i>And Mandalore is chosen
as neutral ground</i>

24
00:00:30,535 --> 00:00:32,578
<i>for these precarious meetings.</i>

25
00:00:32,620 --> 00:00:38,125
<i>Tensions run high as many hold hope
for these important negotiations.</i>

26
00:00:38,209 --> 00:00:41,003
The Republic recognizes
the tragedy of war.

27
00:00:41,087 --> 00:00:44,048
But there is nothing we can change
that has already occurred.

28
00:00:44,131 --> 00:00:46,300
Say it aloud before this gathering,

29
00:00:46,342 --> 00:00:50,930
as representative for Chancellor Palpatine,
that you declare without reservation

30
00:00:50,972 --> 00:00:53,307
the Separatist State legitimate.

31
00:00:57,228 --> 00:01:00,940
I have something to say
about the legitimacy of the Separatists.

32
00:01:02,024 --> 00:01:03,859
Why is Lux Bonteri here?

33
00:01:03,943 --> 00:01:06,821
What could he possibly have to say?

34
00:01:06,904 --> 00:01:08,155
He was not invited.

35
00:01:08,239 --> 00:01:11,117
You didn't mention that Lux Bonteri
would be here.

36
00:01:11,158 --> 00:01:12,827
I didn't know.

37
00:01:21,836 --> 00:01:25,506
I stand before you, son of Mina Bonteri,

38
00:01:25,590 --> 00:01:29,343
loyal Separatist, a patriot, a friend.

39
00:01:34,181 --> 00:01:37,101
It has come to my attention
that my mother was murdered

40
00:01:37,184 --> 00:01:39,353
by Count Dooku in cold blood.

41
00:01:39,395 --> 00:01:41,397
That is a lie!

42
00:01:41,480 --> 00:01:43,524
Remove this traitor immediately.

43
00:01:46,027 --> 00:01:48,070
I will not be silenced.

44
00:01:48,154 --> 00:01:49,697
Stop this!

45
00:01:49,739 --> 00:01:52,700
We would ask you to respect
that we deal with this matter ourselves.

46
00:01:52,742 --> 00:01:55,077
No! Dooku is deceiving you.

47
00:01:55,536 --> 00:01:58,039
You will all be betrayed
just like my mother.

48
00:01:58,122 --> 00:02:01,792
I apologize for such a rude interruption.

49
00:02:01,876 --> 00:02:03,294
Please let us continue.

50
00:02:05,504 --> 00:02:08,758
We can't just let them take him.
He'll be killed.

51
00:02:08,841 --> 00:02:11,886
Do what you can, Ahsoka, but be discreet.

52
00:02:46,754 --> 00:02:52,343
<i>Those are some rather strong
accusations you have levied against me.</i>

53
00:02:52,426 --> 00:02:54,804
You know what you did, Dooku.

54
00:02:54,887 --> 00:02:58,349
<i>Do I? I've done a lot of things, young man.</i>

55
00:02:58,432 --> 00:03:01,602
<i>And choose to remember them
in order of importance.</i>

56
00:03:01,686 --> 00:03:06,315
<i>The death of your mother
seems to have escaped me.</i>

57
00:03:06,399 --> 00:03:08,442
I will have my revenge.

58
00:03:09,402 --> 00:03:13,197
<i>I think it is time we reacquaint
the young senator with his mother.</i>

59
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,783
<i>Kill him.</i>

60
00:03:19,203 --> 00:03:20,287
Ahsoka?

61
00:03:25,126 --> 00:03:28,546
Lux, I think it's time to go. Don't you?

62
00:03:33,384 --> 00:03:35,636
Artoo, fire up the engines. We're leaving.

63
00:03:43,894 --> 00:03:44,979
Run.

64
00:03:52,027 --> 00:03:53,320
Hurry! Hurry!

65
00:03:53,404 --> 00:03:56,824
-Ahsoka, I appreciate your help, but...
-Keep moving.

66
00:04:02,621 --> 00:04:05,833
Captain Taggart,
we've got incoming clankers.

67
00:04:05,875 --> 00:04:08,210
We'll cover you, sir.

68
00:04:30,024 --> 00:04:32,193
<i>Ahsoka, Padmé just contacted me.</i>

69
00:04:32,234 --> 00:04:35,571
<i>She told me the peace negotiations
have all but collapsed. Where are you?</i>

70
00:04:35,654 --> 00:04:39,200
I'm en route to Coruscant, Master.
I have Lux Bonteri with me.

71
00:04:39,241 --> 00:04:41,869
Master Jedi, I'm sorry
if I've caused you any trouble.

72
00:04:41,911 --> 00:04:42,953
It's nothing.

73
00:04:43,412 --> 00:04:45,623
You will be safe now with the Republic.

74
00:04:47,291 --> 00:04:50,169
<i>All right.
Bring Bonteri to Coruscant immediately.</i>

75
00:04:50,211 --> 00:04:51,754
<i>We'll discuss giving him amnesty.</i>

76
00:04:51,837 --> 00:04:53,047
Yes, Master.

77
00:04:54,632 --> 00:04:57,760
-I can't go with you, Ahsoka.
-What?

78
00:04:57,843 --> 00:05:00,471
I told you, I have a plan.

79
00:05:01,847 --> 00:05:04,350
Shooting me is not going to be part of it.

80
00:05:04,391 --> 00:05:07,686
What are you doing with a gun anyhow?
You're not a fighter.

81
00:05:07,728 --> 00:05:09,730
I'm no longer a Separatist either.

82
00:05:09,814 --> 00:05:11,315
I won't join the Republic.

83
00:05:11,398 --> 00:05:13,609
What other options do you have?

84
00:05:13,692 --> 00:05:15,903
There is a different way.

85
00:05:15,945 --> 00:05:17,947
I understand everything
that you've been through.

86
00:05:18,030 --> 00:05:20,282
I understand you feel alone.

87
00:05:20,366 --> 00:05:22,785
But the Republic will help you.

88
00:05:22,868 --> 00:05:24,578
Like they helped my mother?

89
00:05:25,704 --> 00:05:27,998
I've already made contact
with a group on Carlac

90
00:05:28,082 --> 00:05:30,459
who are noble
and are allied with my cause.

91
00:05:30,543 --> 00:05:32,628
And what cause is that?

92
00:05:32,711 --> 00:05:34,213
To kill Dooku.

93
00:05:35,506 --> 00:05:38,759
The only one you're going to get killed
is yourself.

94
00:05:40,135 --> 00:05:43,013
I'm sorry, but I'm taking you to Coruscant.

95
00:05:43,097 --> 00:05:45,599
You're plan hasn't exactly been
well thought out, Lux.

96
00:05:45,683 --> 00:05:49,103
Without me, how did you think
you were going to escape those droids?

97
00:05:49,186 --> 00:05:50,354
Like this.

98
00:05:52,189 --> 00:05:53,941
I'm sorry, Ahsoka.

99
00:06:02,575 --> 00:06:06,787
It seems Ahsoka is quite exhausted.
She probably should sleep it off.

100
00:06:20,551 --> 00:06:21,802
Lux?

101
00:06:23,429 --> 00:06:24,597
Lux?

102
00:06:28,058 --> 00:06:30,561
Where are my lightsabers?

103
00:06:35,816 --> 00:06:37,318
Lux!

104
00:06:37,359 --> 00:06:41,322
Artoo, take a look around
and see if you can find where Lux hid them.

105
00:06:41,405 --> 00:06:44,658
I'm going to have a little chat
with Mr. Bonteri.

106
00:06:53,208 --> 00:06:57,796
Lux! Lux, where are we?
And what did you do with my lightsabers?

107
00:06:57,838 --> 00:07:00,090
You should've stayed on the ship.

108
00:07:11,268 --> 00:07:13,896
Hey, kid. You're late.

109
00:07:14,355 --> 00:07:16,106
Death Watch.

110
00:07:32,790 --> 00:07:34,583
Did you get us what we need?

111
00:07:34,667 --> 00:07:37,044
Yes, I have the information with me.

112
00:07:37,670 --> 00:07:39,004
Who's this?

113
00:07:39,046 --> 00:07:40,547
I'm his...

114
00:07:40,589 --> 00:07:42,633
I'm his betrothed.

115
00:07:44,551 --> 00:07:45,928
Right. Right.

116
00:07:46,303 --> 00:07:47,763
Betrothed?

117
00:07:50,182 --> 00:07:52,476
Little skinny, isn't she?

118
00:07:54,186 --> 00:07:56,313
She serves her purpose.

119
00:08:00,818 --> 00:08:01,986
We leave now.

120
00:08:02,069 --> 00:08:03,612
The snow is coming.

121
00:08:03,696 --> 00:08:05,572
What have you gotten us into?

122
00:08:05,656 --> 00:08:07,491
It's all under control.

123
00:08:10,828 --> 00:08:13,914
These are the Death Watch.
They're Mandalorian terrorists.

124
00:08:13,998 --> 00:08:15,249
- They'll kill us both.
- Are you coming?

125
00:08:15,749 --> 00:08:17,251
Yes.

126
00:08:17,292 --> 00:08:18,919
Uh, I should stay with the ship.

127
00:08:19,003 --> 00:08:21,380
No. You're coming, too.

128
00:09:29,156 --> 00:09:30,783
The boss will see you in there.

129
00:09:38,290 --> 00:09:40,501
Don't ruin my plan, okay?

130
00:09:40,542 --> 00:09:42,336
Plan? What plan?

131
00:09:42,836 --> 00:09:44,838
This is a ho lot race device.

132
00:09:44,922 --> 00:09:48,133
It can identify the origin
of any holo transmission.

133
00:09:48,175 --> 00:09:51,845
I knew if I accused Dooku of murder,
I would be brought to face him.

134
00:09:51,929 --> 00:09:53,889
Well, it worked.

135
00:09:53,972 --> 00:09:56,391
And I now know Dooku's exact location.

136
00:09:56,475 --> 00:09:59,561
If Death Watch moves quick enough
we can destroy him.

137
00:09:59,645 --> 00:10:01,563
Is that enough of a plan for you?

138
00:10:01,647 --> 00:10:04,399
This is not some idealistic political group!

139
00:10:04,483 --> 00:10:07,027
They will take the information and kill you.

140
00:10:07,903 --> 00:10:09,947
I knew you wouldn't understand.

141
00:10:10,030 --> 00:10:13,867
The Death Watch are murderers!
Sworn to destroy Jedi.

142
00:10:13,909 --> 00:10:16,120
You don't know what you're doing ! This...

143
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,665
Am I interrupting something?

144
00:10:21,083 --> 00:10:23,877
No. Of course not. We were just...

145
00:10:25,170 --> 00:10:27,005
It's time to talk business.

146
00:10:29,007 --> 00:10:31,468
Tell your woman to leave us.

147
00:10:32,052 --> 00:10:33,303
Of course.

148
00:10:37,349 --> 00:10:40,811
Now, give me what I want.

149
00:10:41,645 --> 00:10:43,939
When I know that you will use it correctly.

150
00:10:44,022 --> 00:10:46,316
Don't toy with me, boy.

151
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:48,235
You see this scar?

152
00:10:48,318 --> 00:10:51,363
It was a parting gift from Count Dooku.

153
00:10:51,405 --> 00:10:54,199
If you question my resolve
to destroy him again,

154
00:10:54,241 --> 00:10:56,577
I will give you one just like it.

155
00:10:57,077 --> 00:10:59,746
This device will tell you his location.

156
00:11:01,832 --> 00:11:05,043
Good. That was painless, wasn't it?

157
00:11:05,419 --> 00:11:07,671
Now, let's celebrate.

158
00:11:20,601 --> 00:11:22,102
Repair these droids

159
00:11:22,186 --> 00:11:26,523
so we can use them
for target practice again.

160
00:11:32,571 --> 00:11:35,657
Please reassemble us.

161
00:11:35,741 --> 00:11:38,493
Please reassemble us.

162
00:11:38,577 --> 00:11:42,789
We are battle droids no longer.
Now we are slaves.

163
00:11:46,460 --> 00:11:48,128
Please reassemble us.

164
00:12:00,807 --> 00:12:03,060
Try that again and I will...

165
00:12:03,143 --> 00:12:07,648
You don't want to make them angry.
They are far from rational.

166
00:12:08,482 --> 00:12:12,069
Believe me, you have no idea.

167
00:12:13,487 --> 00:12:15,781
-What's your name?
-Try la.

168
00:12:15,822 --> 00:12:18,992
I'm Ahsoka. Where are you from?

169
00:12:19,076 --> 00:12:21,370
We were kidnapped from a nearby town.

170
00:12:21,453 --> 00:12:26,667
We are a simple people. We trust easily.
And we were betrayed.

171
00:12:27,751 --> 00:12:32,381
We feast. Prepare the food.
Your masters are hungry.

172
00:12:55,195 --> 00:12:56,530
Hungry?

173
00:12:57,322 --> 00:13:00,367
Careful not to choke on your stupidity.

174
00:13:02,452 --> 00:13:06,581
I see your woman has fit in well.
Now, how will you fit in?

175
00:13:06,665 --> 00:13:09,042
All I want is Dooku dead.

176
00:13:09,084 --> 00:13:10,419
Vizsla.

177
00:13:13,839 --> 00:13:17,718
Chieftain Pieter,
I don't remember summoning you.

178
00:13:19,303 --> 00:13:24,558
You have taken our women, stolen our food
and threatened us for too long.

179
00:13:25,392 --> 00:13:28,562
Brave for you to come here
with such bold words.

180
00:13:29,438 --> 00:13:32,232
You are no longer welcome here.

181
00:13:32,274 --> 00:13:36,528
Well, if our presence here isn't welcome,
we'll make ready to leave.

182
00:13:40,991 --> 00:13:43,660
And you'll return our people to us?

183
00:13:43,744 --> 00:13:48,081
Yes, sunrise tomorrow. You have my word.

184
00:13:49,416 --> 00:13:52,753
Very well. We'll be waiting.

185
00:13:58,925 --> 00:14:02,596
You see? They're not the butchers
you make them out to be.

186
00:14:25,452 --> 00:14:27,454
You have kept your word.

187
00:14:28,121 --> 00:14:31,208
We are very grateful
for your understanding.

188
00:14:38,090 --> 00:14:40,300
I am a man of my word.

189
00:14:40,342 --> 00:14:43,470
Here is your granddaughter, as promised.

190
00:14:43,553 --> 00:14:44,554
-No!
-Try la!

191
00:14:49,059 --> 00:14:51,645
Kill them. Kill them all.

192
00:14:54,773 --> 00:14:58,735
No! Our village. Run for your lives!

193
00:15:03,115 --> 00:15:07,619
Save them, Ahsoka. Save them.
Save my people.

194
00:15:09,830 --> 00:15:12,124
Why? What are you doing?

195
00:15:12,165 --> 00:15:15,377
Never let the weak tell you what to do.

196
00:15:16,169 --> 00:15:18,547
Welcome to Death Watch.

197
00:15:54,666 --> 00:15:57,544
Now what do we have here?

198
00:15:57,627 --> 00:16:00,630
I think we've caught ourselves a Jedi.

199
00:16:03,049 --> 00:16:04,926
Drag her back to camp.

200
00:16:17,314 --> 00:16:21,359
Thank you, friend. How can we repay you?

201
00:16:42,255 --> 00:16:45,300
Rescue your friends. How?

202
00:16:47,719 --> 00:16:49,429
I compute.

203
00:16:49,513 --> 00:16:51,932
I will prepare the others.

204
00:16:59,606 --> 00:17:01,691
Now, Lux Bonteri,

205
00:17:02,234 --> 00:17:05,946
this does not look good.
This does not look good at all.

206
00:17:06,947 --> 00:17:11,785
I asked you to join us in good faith
and you bring a Jedi into our camp.

207
00:17:11,826 --> 00:17:15,372
She wasn't meant to be here.
Please let her go.

208
00:17:15,455 --> 00:17:17,958
I'm afraid that's not an option.

209
00:17:17,999 --> 00:17:21,461
I believed you had honor,
but you're just murderers.

210
00:17:21,503 --> 00:17:23,505
No better than Dooku.

211
00:17:23,588 --> 00:17:25,465
You call us murderers?

212
00:17:25,549 --> 00:17:29,427
And yet it was your own lust for revenge
that made you seek us out.

213
00:17:29,469 --> 00:17:31,805
I wanted justice for my mother's death.

214
00:17:31,846 --> 00:17:33,473
And you shall have it.

215
00:17:33,515 --> 00:17:35,809
But the Jedi are no different from Dooku

216
00:17:35,850 --> 00:17:40,355
and this one shall pay in part
for their crimes against Mandalore.

217
00:17:40,438 --> 00:17:44,150
So you see it's not murder at all.
It's like you say.

218
00:17:44,818 --> 00:17:46,403
It's justice.

219
00:17:50,740 --> 00:17:52,158
Ahsoka, now!

220
00:17:53,868 --> 00:17:55,203
Thanks, buddy.

221
00:18:00,125 --> 00:18:03,920
Stop! The Jedi is mine.

222
00:18:04,004 --> 00:18:06,256
Lux, get to the ship.

223
00:18:28,028 --> 00:18:29,863
I guess Artoo made some friends.

224
00:19:06,483 --> 00:19:07,734
Not bad, Jedi.

225
00:19:08,485 --> 00:19:10,779
I didn't miss.

226
00:19:17,077 --> 00:19:18,370
Ahsoka!

227
00:19:23,208 --> 00:19:25,085
Don't let them escape.

228
00:19:55,448 --> 00:19:57,367
That's two I owe you.

229
00:20:52,839 --> 00:20:55,508
No one followed us. God job, Artoo.

230
00:20:56,968 --> 00:21:00,555
What do you mean
the escape pod has been activated?

231
00:21:00,638 --> 00:21:02,849
Lux! Artoo, the ship is yours.

232
00:21:10,148 --> 00:21:12,692
Lux. Lux, what are you doing?

233
00:21:14,569 --> 00:21:16,112
I can't go with you, Ahsoka.

234
00:21:18,072 --> 00:21:19,574
You know that.

235
00:21:19,657 --> 00:21:21,826
But we can try...

236
00:21:22,619 --> 00:21:25,538
Try to change things together.

237
00:21:26,915 --> 00:21:29,709
We make a pretty good team, don't we?

238
00:21:31,836 --> 00:21:35,423
Don't worry. We'll meet again. I promise.

239
00:21:41,387 --> 00:21:43,306
Be careful, Lux.

240
00:21:43,330 --> 00:21:48,330
http://hiqve.com/

